(11, 1, '2015-05-29 15:21:18', '2015-05-29 15:21:18', '[caption id="attachment_22" align="alignright" width="208"]<a href="http://rajib.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Rangamati-Waterfront_ProfilePhoto1.jpg"><img class="wp-image-22 size-medium" src="http://rajib.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Rangamati-Waterfront_ProfilePhoto1-208x300.jpg" alt="Rajib_ProfilePhoto" width="208" height="300" /></a> at Rangamati Waterfront Resort[/caption]\r\n\r\nHi, I''m Rajib... currently working as a Software Engineer at <a href="http://www.eyeball.com" target="_blank">Eyeball International Ltd</a>. I have completed my graduation on Computer Science &amp; Engineering from <a href="http://www.sust.edu" target="_blank">Shahjalal University of Scient &amp; Technology.</a> My main objective is to be in touch with new technologies, enhance knowledge and implement my innovative ideas and skills.\r\n\r\nI am now living in Dhaka city(Capital of Bangladesh), but actually I have come from another city called Narsingdi and it''s my home district. After completing my SSC and HSC, I have moved from this place. Whenever I get time, I try to spend time with my family.\r\n\r\nI''m interested in computer science, technologies, sports, games, movies and musics. Computers first appeared in my life when I was twelve. I started playing games after getting my new computer. I like all sort of games like Sports, Racing, Strategy, Action, Adventure, Shooting, Puzzles etc. After a long time I understood that, I could do lot more things using this computer like <em>Programming</em>, <em>Developing</em>, <em>Designing</em> etc. When I started learning these captivating topics, computer became my best friend. I can''t  spend a single day without a computer. Now I am capable of writing <strong>desktop applications</strong>, <strong>mobile apps</strong>, <strong>server programs</strong> &amp; <strong>web pages</strong> etc.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_34" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="wp-image-34 size-medium" src="http://rajib.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Volleyball_Award-300x228.jpg" alt="Volleyball_Award" width="300" height="228" /> Receiving runner-up award for Inter Department Volleyball Tournament at SUST.[/caption]\r\n\r\nI have always been good at sports. I like playing cricket, football, badminton, volleyball &amp; table tennis. I have participated in many sport tournaments and achieved numerous awards and trophies. I played for football team <em><strong>"The Vikings"</strong></em>  in 2012 and <em><strong>"Core i7"</strong></em> in 2013 in Sports SUST football championship. I also played for the cricket team named <em><strong>"The Barrels"</strong></em> in 2014 in Sport SUST cricket tournament. I participated in First Division Volleyball Tournament 2 times which were held in Sylhet and I played for the team named <em><strong>"City Sporting Club"</strong></em>. I had outstanding performances in many Badminton tournaments and achieved several trophies and awards. My favorite intellectual game is Chess. I was one of the best Chess players in my university but I never played it professionally.\r\n\r\nI want to be truthful, honest and a good person. I never try to hurt anybody with my behavior and attitude . My dream is to do something special so that people can know me separately.', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2015-07-04 20:03:08', '2015-07-04 20:03:08', '', 0, 'http://rajib.me/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
